rows.label: qst400204_msg0002
rows.name:
But the grown-ups do seem to be
talking about secret complicated
stuff a lot lately...

rows.label: qst400204_msg0003
rows.name:
Apparently there are some kind of
dangerous people causing trouble...

rows.label: qst400204_msg0004
rows.name:
It's only been ten years since the war
between Superbia and Invidia ended.
Why would they stir up more trouble?

rows.label: qst400204_msg0005
rows.name:
It sounds like a real pain...
I hope the Superbian soldiers
will be able to protect us.
